'''飓风佛罗伦萨'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Florence}}）是1953年9月吹袭[[佛罗里达西北狭长地带|佛罗里达西北狭长地带]]的一场小型[[北大西洋热带气旋|大西洋飓风]]，也是[[1953年大西洋飓风季|1953年大西洋飓风季]]的第八场热带风暴和第五场飓风，源自9月23日[[牙买加|牙买加]]附近西加勒比海的一股[[东风波|东风波]]。气旋在牙买加降下暴雨，之后又对[[古巴|古巴]]西部构成破坏。风暴很快就在[[尤卡坦海峡|尤卡坦海峡]]上空增强成飓风，经过[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]北部期间[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]提升到每小时205公里。9月26日，佛罗伦萨吹袭[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]西部人烟稀少的区域，不久便转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。

飓风造成421套房屋受损，另有三套被毁。狂风将三个避难所的屋顶摧毁，致使一人受伤。佛罗里达州[[阿巴拉契科拉_(佛罗里达州)|阿巴拉契科拉]]同外界的交通一度中断。整场风暴没有造成人员丧生，损失总额约为20万美元（1953年[[美元|美元]]，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|200000|1953}}}}美元）。转变成温带气旋后，系统继续向东北移动，沿途产生降水，最终于9月28日在[[新英格兰|新英格兰]]东南方向逐渐消散。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Florence 1953 track.png}}
9月21日，一股[[东风波|东风波]]经[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]进入东[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]。东风波总体向西移动，于9月23日在[[牙买加|牙买加]]东南方向约160公里海域催生出热带风暴。气旋获名“佛罗伦萨”（{{lang|en|Florence}}）并稳步增强，但一直到9月24日才发展出层次分明的环流，并且当天还在[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]和[[古巴|古巴]]最西端之间的[[尤卡坦海峡|尤卡坦海峡]]达到飓风标准。<ref name="mwr">{{cite web | author = Grady Norton, U.S. Weather Bureau | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 1953-12 | accessdate = 2017-02-13 | title = Hurricanes of 1953 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303221428/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1953.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1953.pdf | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] }}</ref>

转向北上进入[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]后，风暴迅速强化，[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]估计风速达到每小时205至225公里<ref name="mwr" />，大西洋飓风数据库的记录则认定气旋[[最大持续风速|最强风力时速]]为205公里，最低[[气压|气压]]968[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，28.59[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | deadurl = no }}</ref>。不过，飓风所在海域的船只所测风速不足，表明上述最高强度可能比实际情况偏高<ref name="mwr" />。9月26日，佛罗伦萨开始因行经洋面[[海面温度|海水]]和大气温度降低而快速减弱<ref name="up927">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | agency = United Press | date = 1953-09-27 | title = Hurricane Florence Dies Over Northwest Florida | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=888&dat=19530927&id=KMcKAAAAIBAJ&sjid=VE8DAAAAIBAJ&pg=5395,4716021 | newspaper = St. Petersburg Times | accessdate = 2017-02-13 | archive-date = 2021-08-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210802100244/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=888&dat=19530927&id=KMcKAAAAIBAJ&sjid=VE8DAAAAIBAJ&pg=5395%2C4716021 }}</ref>。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]当天下午18点左右，气旋以持续风速约每小时130公里强度从佛罗里达州[[华尔顿堡滩_(佛罗里达州)|华尔顿堡滩]]与[[巴拿马市海滩_(佛罗里达州)|巴拿马市海滩]]间[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，登陆点附近人烟稀少。上岸约六小时后，飓风已在佛罗里达州、[[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]]和[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]边界附近转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。<ref name="mwr" /><ref name="HURDAT" />风暴残留沿[[冷锋|冷锋]]转向东北，经过乔治亚州后从[[萨凡纳|萨凡纳]]附近进入大西洋。佛罗伦萨在南、北卡罗莱纳州近海沿海岸线平行移动，最终于9月28日在[[新英格兰|新英格兰]]东南海域逐渐消散。<ref name="rain">{{cite web | author = David M. Roth | date = 2008-09-23 | title = Hurricane Florence - September 24-28, 1953 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2017-02-14 | archivedate = 2014-12-22 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/florence1953.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141222032847/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/florence1953.html }}</ref><ref name="HURDAT" />

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Florence_1953_rainfall.gif|thumb]]

风暴发展之初就在牙买加降下多达250毫米雨量，导致多个村庄同外界的交通中断，部分道路封闭<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | agency = Associated Press | date = 1953-09-24 | title = Jamaica Warned of Nearby Hurricane | newspaper = St. Joseph Gazette | accessdate = 2017-02-13 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=OilaAAAAIBAJ&sjid=BUwNAAAAIBAJ&pg=5763,4876604&dq=hurricane&hl=en | archive-date = 2020-12-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201202140314/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=OilaAAAAIBAJ&sjid=BUwNAAAAIBAJ&pg=5763%2C4876604&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。飓风存在早期就在古巴西岸沿线产生狂风巨浪，局部地区受到严重破坏<ref name="en">{{cite book | author = David Longshore | title = Encyclopedia of hurricanes, typhoons, and cyclones | page = 186 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=8kXwskQHBLoC&lpg=PA186&ots=qCMhZG6c8U&dq=Hurricane%20Florence%201953%20gulf%20coast&pg=PA186#v=onepage&q&f=false | accessdate = 2017-02-13 | year = 2008 | publisher = Facts on File, Inc. | archive-date = 2019-11-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191129174334/https://books.google.com/books?id=8kXwskQHBLoC&lpg=PA186&ots=qCMhZG6c8U&dq=Hurricane%20Florence%201953%20gulf%20coast&pg=PA186#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。气旋登陆[[美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区|美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区]]前，[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]发出[[热带气旋警告|热带气旋警告]]，建议人员疏散，所以全美没有人员丧生，受伤人数也很少<ref name="mwr" />。佛罗里达州和阿拉巴马州启用[[美国国民警卫队|国民警卫队]]，防止重大灾情发生，最后的实际情况表明这只是虚惊一场。[[美国空军|美国空军]]将数百架飞机转移到更安全的地点。此外，[[美国海岸警卫队|海岸警卫队]]沿海岸线向人们发出警告，做好应对飓风来袭的准备。<ref name="tusc">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = The Tuscaloosa News | date = 1953-09-26 | title = Powerful Hurricane Sweeps Fla. Coast | agency = Associated Press | accessdate = 2017-02-13 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=NQcdAAAAIBAJ&sjid=OJgEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6769,2629896&dq=hurricane&hl=en | archive-date = 2021-08-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210802100313/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=NQcdAAAAIBAJ&sjid=OJgEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6769%2C2629896&dq=hurricane&hl=en }}</ref>佛罗里达州[[巴拿马城_(佛罗里达州)|巴拿马城]]约有一万人撤离<ref name="pc">{{cite journal | author = E. L. Quarantelli | date = 1982-05 | title = Inventory of Disaster Field Studies in the Social and Behaviroal Sciences 1919 - 1979 | page = D-9 | publisher = University of Delaware | accessdate = 2017-02-14 | url = http://udspace.udel.edu/bitstream/handle/19716/1309/MR32.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170214141118/http://udspace.udel.edu/bitstream/handle/19716/1309/MR32.pdf | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2017-02-14 | format = PDF }}</ref>。[[北美中部时区|美国中部夏令时]]9月26日下午16点，美国国家气象局驻[[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]办事处将所有警告取消<ref name="up927" />。从9月25日早上开始，海岸警卫队的一艘船在近海停留18小时同气旋搏斗，直到9月26日凌晨为止<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = St. Petersburg Times | date = 1953-09-28 | title = Hurricane Florence Given Bad Time By Coast Guard's Gobs | accessdate = 2017-02-13 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=888&dat=19530928&id=KccKAAAAIBAJ&sjid=VE8DAAAAIBAJ&pg=3994,6092901 | archive-date = 2021-08-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210802100324/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=888&dat=19530928&id=KccKAAAAIBAJ&sjid=VE8DAAAAIBAJ&pg=3994%2C6092901 }}</ref>。

[[埃格林空军基地|埃格林空军基地]]所测风速最高，达每小时135公里<ref name="up927" />。虽然风暴是在佛罗里达州登陆，但却是以阿拉巴马州[[骆克_(阿拉巴马州)|骆克]]降雨量最高，达374毫米<ref name="rain" />。飓风中心两侧的[[雨带|雨带]]非常强劲，产生的降水也最多，每小时降雨量一度超过38毫米<ref>{{cite journal |author=Sterling C. Gilbert and N.E. LaSeur |volume=14 |journal=Journal of Meteorology |archivedate=2016-03-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304130707/https://myweb.fsu.edu/jelsner/extspace/GilbertLaSeur_1957.pdf |deadurl=yes |url=https://myweb.fsu.edu/jelsner/extspace/GilbertLaSeur_1957.pdf |accessdate=2017-02-14 |format=PDF |title=A study of the rainfall patterns and some related features in a dissipating hurricane |pages=18–27 |date=1957-02 |doi=10.1175/0095-9634-14.1.18 }}</ref>。巴拿马城在三小时内降下93毫米雨量<ref name="tusc" />。狂风暴雨致使佛罗里达西北狭长地带和阿拉巴马州东南部的农作物受到轻度破坏<ref name="mwr" />。狂风把三个避难所的屋顶摧毁，其中一个位于埃格林空军基地，两个位于[[克雷斯特韦_(佛罗里达州)|克雷斯特韦]]，在此躲避的人员被迫转移，期间有一人受伤。克雷斯特韦另有九套房屋的屋顶被毁。高达4.3米的巨浪导致巴拿马城一座渔业码头约30米部分受损。大浪还把[[98号美国国道|98号美国国道]]位于[[阿巴拉契科拉_(佛罗里达州)|阿巴拉契科拉]]附近部分路段冲毁，致使多条电缆断裂，市区同外界的交通中断。<ref name="up927" />

飓风最强风力吹袭的地区人烟相对稀少，所以美国整体所受破坏程度很轻，估计损失总额约为20万美元（1953美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|200000|1953}}}}美元）<ref name="mwr" />。阿拉巴马州部分地点降下暴雨，最高降雨总量为221毫米，距[[蒙哥马利_(阿拉巴马州)|蒙哥马利]]1892年所创24小时雨量纪录还差25毫米。蒙哥马利导致下水道不堪重负，部分民居和汽车被淹。飓风共导致当地约4000人失去供电。<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | agency = Associated Press | date = 1953-09-28 | title = Hurricane Brushes State; Near-Record Rains Follow | accessdate = 2017-02-13 | newspaper = Times Daily | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=SAUsAAAAIBAJ&sjid=lcYEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6374,7848186&dq=hurricane&hl=en | archive-date = 2021-08-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210802100333/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=SAUsAAAAIBAJ&sjid=lcYEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6374%2C7848186&dq=hurricane&hl=en }}</ref>佛罗伦萨经过[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]期间与冷锋共同影响，所以中心附近及左侧的降雨量最高<ref name="rain" />。

